ile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"放心一定會頂到煲底個日因為每次發完夢啲活力都返晒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都有諗過休息一排 但當我一休息個陣就發生好多令我好嬲嘅事 尤其係十月一佢只係一個細我一年嘅細路但比我更加勇敢 真係搞到我好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每次都忍唔到唔出黎保護啲比我細嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有平衡下我温書同發夢嘅時間 希望可以守護到我前途之餘更加可以守護到我嘅家 大家煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d088b81439743297a432a104229bf4d13a3604","tid":1663580,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22a3ea9b3e7ec267dde032f8fccda013433b58e2","tid":1663580,"uid":331605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1da5188f289b43bbec77c9b3843dec29e94d3f7f","tid":1663580,"uid":304344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46130a28c06aff8ce1473681fcfef1c886794960","tid":1663580,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:28:56.000Z","msg":"屋企深紅係好難頂，咁多啲去自修室溫書啦，考試要緊，影響你前途，以後香港就靠你地，發夢大家一齊發，齊上齊落，頂住。但唔掂就要睇醫生，俾啲安眠葯你等你瞓到覺都好，休息好緊要！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"加油， 齊上齊落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都要加油呀 煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410ff89b2e85145330fbff4dde7dc21f09d1d7b0","tid":1663580,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1da5188f289b43bbec77c9b3843dec29e94d3f7f","tid":1663580,"uid":304344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46130a28c06aff8ce1473681fcfef1c886794960","tid":1663580,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:28:56.000Z","msg":"屋企深紅係好難頂，咁多啲去自修室溫書啦，考試要緊，影響你前途，以後香港就靠你地，發夢大家一齊發，齊上齊落，頂住。但唔掂就要睇醫生，俾啲安眠葯你等你瞓到覺都好，休息好緊要！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"係好難頂 但次次一諗到光復香港個日個兩條廢老就可以收皮就好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻更加有動力温書同發夢  到時收佢地皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ac998a354039893a5c8b125da19acf37bea59e","tid":1663580,"uid":140337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:09:13.000Z","msg":"巴打加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007bf0c8de8d52bf8a26a6ab893fae95c3b26535","tid":1663580,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:33:24.000Z","msg":"我情況有少少同你相似<br />\n不過我就已經番緊工<br />\n自己一個搬左出去住<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月<br />\n每日放工、每次發完夢自己番去對住4幅牆<br />\n果種壓抑都真係好難受<br />\n明明自己出左不自殺聲明，但係都有諗過自殺就算<br />\n不過諗到如果出左聲明，一陣自殺咪搞到個聲明冇哂公信力，所以都頂住<br />\n平時幾灰都好，都要扮積極<br />\n推行動post，簽聯署，發夢就自己周圍游走<br />\n<br />\n但係有時到半夜果陣，望住塊牆<br />\n望望下個胃會隱隱作痛<br />\n唯有食下煙等自己冇咁focus <br />\n<br />\n希望所有樓主同所有手足都平安啦"},{"pid":"fb01036343056c61ecdc59bf045d8d92e502267a","tid":1663580,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:00:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06395295e512b60acec043abcc149a70d073739a","tid":1663580,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:04:44.000Z","msg":"習慣與病同行 知道自己點都係會焦慮 點都會成日想死 無時無刻都灰到仆街 <br />\n令自己不斷分心同係屋企長期帶耳機塞住耳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21fd5f105b00df493bc24113daf7e4761b67978","tid":1663580,"uid":105490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:05:33.000Z","msg":"唔好再參與<br />\n真係會自殺既"},{"pid":"343025a3d0c43dad5b24a48637090ed386ee540d","tid":1663580,"uid":30661